name: Feed or food
description:
Collect food points and go into the monster's mouth in the end of the track before time runs out. Beware: If you haven't collected enough food, the monster will not be satisfied and ends up eating you instead.

  • Steer: Arrow keys / A & D
  • Jump: Space
  • Restart: R
  • Pause: Esc
